---
---

<section class="test-section">

  <div class="test-inner">

    <!-- Left: main quote -->
    <div class="test-left">
      <div class="test-quote-mark">❝</div>

      <div class="test-avatar-block">
        <div class="test-avatar">JR</div>
        <div class="test-avatar-info">
          <strong>Juan Rodríguez</strong>
          <span>Taller Deportivo Tucumán</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="test-quote">
        Antes tardaba casi 3 horas para armar un equipo de 18 chicos. Con SubliFlow lo hago en 10 minutos. Lo más valioso no es el tiempo — es que ya no me equivoco más en los números ni en las tallas.
      </blockquote>

      <div class="test-chips">
        <span class="test-chip">3 hrs → 10 min</span>
        <span class="test-chip">0 errores de impresión</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="test-divider"></div>

    <!-- Right: mini testimonials stack -->
    <div class="test-right">

      <div class="test-mini-header">
        <span class="test-tag">Testimonios</span>
        <p>Lo que dicen los talleres que ya usan SubliFlow</p>
      </div>

      <div class="test-mini-list">

        <div class="test-mini">
          <div class="mini-avatar">MP</div>
          <div class="mini-content">
            <blockquote>"La configuración de base se reutiliza. El segundo equipo me llevó 5 minutos."</blockquote>
            <span class="mini-author">Marta Pérez — Confecciones Deportivas MP</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="test-mini">
          <div class="mini-avatar cyan">LC</div>
          <div class="mini-content">
            <blockquote>"El plugin de Illustrator hace todo solo. No puedo creer que no existiera antes."</blockquote>
            <span class="mini-author">Luis Cano — Studio 9 Uniformes</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="test-mini">
          <div class="mini-avatar coral">AG</div>
          <div class="mini-content">
            <blockquote>"Pasé de 2 equipos por semana a 6. La diferencia es brutal."</blockquote>
            <span class="mini-author">Ana Gómez — Taller Gómez Sporting</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .test-section {
    background: #FFE600;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
  }

  .test-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 3px 1fr;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    min-height: 480px;
  }

  /* ─── Left: main quote ────────────────── */
  .test-left {
    padding: 64px 56px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .test-quote-mark {
    font-size: 96px;
    line-height: 0.7;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #0D0D0D;
    opacity: 0.15;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    margin-bottom: -8px;
  }

  .test-avatar-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .test-avatar {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: #0D0D0D;
    border: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #FFE600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .test-avatar-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .test-avatar-info strong {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0D0D0D;
  }

  .test-avatar-info span {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #555;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .test-quote {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 24px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #0D0D0D;
    font-style: normal;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .test-chips {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .test-chip {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    background: #0D0D0D;
    color: #FFE600;
  }

  /* ─── Divider ─────────────────────────── */
  .test-divider {
    background: #0D0D0D;
    width: 3px;
  }

  /* ─── Right: mini testimonials ────────── */
  .test-right {
    padding: 64px 56px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .test-mini-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .test-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    background: transparent;
    color: #0D0D0D;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .test-mini-header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
  }

  .test-mini-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
  }

  .test-mini {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 24px 24px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #0D0D0D;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .test-mini:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .test-mini:nth-child(even) {
    background: #FFFCF0;
  }

  .mini-avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: #0D0D0D;
    border: 2px solid #0D0D0D;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #FFE600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .mini-avatar.cyan  { background: #00C8B8; color: #0D0D0D; border-color: #00C8B8; }
  .mini-avatar.coral { background: #FF5757; color: #fff;    border-color: #FF5757; }

  .mini-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .mini-content blockquote {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #0D0D0D;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .mini-author {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #888;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ─── Responsive ──────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .test-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto 3px auto;
    }
    .test-divider {
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
    }
    .test-left  { padding: 48px 32px 40px; }
    .test-right { padding: 40px 32px 56px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .test-left  { padding: 40px 20px 32px; }
    .test-right { padding: 32px 20px 48px; }
    .test-quote { font-size: 18px; }
  }
</style>
